&quot;Gimme somethin strong!&quot;, Keliose remarks to the Barkeep who has by now made herself known. <br>
&quot;And what do YOU want?&quot;, she asks Epicurus.<br>
&quot;Oh, Water is fine.&quot;, says Epicurus, snapping out of a daze. <br>
&quot;So anyway, Welcor...&quot;, Keliose starts as he turns to his Barbarian companion. They start joking around, a few times trying to get Epicurus to join in. But Epicurus wasn't paying attention to them... His gaze was fixed solely on the dark figure across the room. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/udrixa.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Drixa</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Barmaid</span><br>  Posts: 30<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(10/20/01 11:39:38 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=12.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hatreds Champion</span><hr size=1> Drixa hurries back to the table with a strong, dark ale, a glass of chilled water, and a silent prayer that there will be no more battles within her bar....<br>
<br>
 <p>Drixa<BR>
Barmaid of the Hero Heart Tavern<BR>
"Pull up a stool, here's an ale to wash the road dust from your throat, and tell me <I>allllllllll</I> about it..."
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/umennelkir.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mennelkir</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_lightning.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 49<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(10/20/01 12:53:50 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=12.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.lordsofdrakova.com/members/mennelkir/mennelkir2.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hatreds Champion</span><hr size=1> There won't be if the dark stranger has anything to do with it.  He feels Epicurus's stare, but does nothing to acknowledge it.  His urge to slaughter the Koada`Dal is restrained by the need to keep his identity a secret.<br>
<br>
The dark man is, however, perturbed enough to take a few more sips of his drink.<br>
<br>
-Vaelis t'Lanshia,<br>
